problem_info.title: 3276. Select Cells in Grid With Maximum Score
test_examples: Example 1: Input: grid = [[1,2,3],[4,3,2],[1,1,1]] Output: 8 Explanation: We can select the cells with values 1, 3, and 4 that are colored above.
Example 2: Input: grid = [[8,7,6],[8,3,2]] Output: 15 Explanation: We can select the cells with values 7 and 8 that are colored above.
